following the injunction ordered by the High Court, stating that a failure to hold the AGM \\\"appears to clearly amount to undue influence by third parties\\\".\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.202787524612988e-15, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8454447172722376e-20, \"text\": \"FAZ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\"}, {\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8454447172722376e-20, \"text\": \"FAZ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\"}, {\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_Justice\", \"score\": 0.9995146953276519, \"rank\": 0.00045168220980103393, \"text\": \"High Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_Justice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_Justice\"}, {\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annual_general_meeting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1292080931107694e-18, \"text\": \"AGM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annual_general_meeting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annual_general_meeting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FIFA's laws prohibit third-party influence in the running of a member association and it has previously suspended nations where governments or courts have been judged to have interfered, such as India in August 2022.\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.202787524612988e-15, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 1169, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8216447200627394, \"rank\": 0.08630204831863471, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The letter added that the cancelled AGM could result in FAZ's suspension, meaning its teams will be unable to compete against other FIFA member nations.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annual_general_meeting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1292080931107694e-18, \"text\": \"AGM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annual_general_meeting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annual_general_meeting\"}, {\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8454447172722376e-20, \"text\": \"FAZ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\"}, {\"begin\": 1323, \"end\": 1327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.202787524612988e-15, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FIFA's letter, sent by member associations officer Kenny Jean-Marie, also \\\"took note with great concern\\\" the charges against FAZ's president and general secretary.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.202787524612988e-15, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 1470, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8454447172722376e-20, \"text\": \"FAZ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The letter requested that FAZ provide FIFA with documents and additional information relating to the case by Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8454447172722376e-20, \"text\": \"FAZ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\"}, {\"begin\": 1547, \"end\": 1551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.202787524612988e-15, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FAZ president Andrew Kamanga, general secretary Reuben Kamanga and two others - Madalitso Kamanga and Jairous Siame - were arrested and charged with money laundering offences, including obtaining money by false pretences and conspiracy to defraud, according to a press release from Zambia's Drug Enforcement Commission (DEC) from Tuesday, April 23.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8454447172722376e-20, \"text\": \"FAZ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\"}, {\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Kamanga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Kamanga\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Kamanga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Kamanga\"}, {\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuben_Kamanga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reuben Kamanga\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuben_Kamanga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuben_Kamanga\"}, {\"begin\": 1910, \"end\": 1916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8373060409055758, \"rank\": 0.19399239507370983, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disasters_Emergency_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9259733827691602, \"rank\": 0.07857108004522727, \"text\": \"DEC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disasters_Emergency_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disasters_Emergency_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The DEC stated that the alleged offences related to the quartet obtaining funds from the government for the non-FAZ pair to travel to the Ivory Coast for the Africa Cup of Nations (AFCON) earlier this year.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1982, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disasters_Emergency_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9259733827691602, \"rank\": 0.07857108004522727, \"text\": \"DEC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disasters_Emergency_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disasters_Emergency_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2116, \"end\": 2127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivory_Coast_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999098772646, \"rank\": 9.01079059262018e-08, \"text\": \"Ivory Coast\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivory_Coast_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivory_Coast_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The investigation revealed approximately \\u00a310,200 was obtained for \\\"allowances\\\" with an additional \\u00a33,000 for return flights.\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  The DEC added the quartet were \\\"due to appear in court soon\\\".\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2330, \"end\": 2333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disasters_Emergency_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9259733827691602, \"rank\": 0.07857108004522727, \"text\": \"DEC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disasters_Emergency_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disasters_Emergency_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All four have denied the charges, per local media.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the arrests and charges, an injunction was filed to Zambia's High Court to prevent FAZ's AGM from happening as planned on Saturday, April 27.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2502, \"end\": 25